Terraform with Kubernetes
Complete Hands-On Lab: Deploy NGINX on Kubernetes using Terraform (AWS EC2)
This lab simulates a real DevOps project where Terraform manages Kubernetes resources.

Project Architecture
AWS EC2 (Ubuntu)
        │
        ▼
   Terraform
        │
        ▼
 Kubernetes Cluster
   (Minikube)
        │
 ┌──────┴──────┐
 ▼             ▼
Namespace    Service
                  │
                  ▼
            NGINX Pod

Project Objective:
Using Terraform:
✅ Connect to Kubernetes
✅ Create Namespace
✅ Create Deployment
✅ Create Service
✅ Verify Application
Prerequisites
AWS Account
EC2 Instance
Ubuntu 22.04
Security Group:
22     SSH
80     HTTP
30000-32767  NodePort
Recommended:
t3.medium
2 CPU
4 GB RAM
